    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >《方圆战争》是一款轻度Rouge塔防游戏</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >游戏玩法</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在白天发展经济，升级科技，建造防线。在夜晚面对敌人的进攻。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3287710/extras/c2c0e827aafd94280ba5a342a4b5f288.poster.avif?t=1731758461\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3287710/extras/c2c0e827aafd94280ba5a342a4b5f288.webm?t=1731758461\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3287710/extras/c2c0e827aafd94280ba5a342a4b5f288.mp4?t=1731758461\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >创新的防御玩法</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >利用防御塔阻拦和攻击敌人，防止其攻击核心</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3287710/extras/824a199019923bb544b4dca5bd64040a.poster.avif?t=1731758461\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3287710/extras/824a199019923bb544b4dca5bd64040a.webm?t=1731758461\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3287710/extras/824a199019923bb544b4dca5bd64040a.mp4?t=1731758461\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >自由构筑体验</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >使用附魔和词条机制强化防御塔，构筑不同种类的防线</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3287710/extras/a6e74da1d9c89c073779d96f3a187333.poster.avif?t=1731758461\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3287710/extras/a6e74da1d9c89c073779d96f3a187333.webm?t=1731758461\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3287710/extras/a6e74da1d9c89c073779d96f3a187333.mp4?t=1731758461\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >丰富的游戏内容</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >35+种不同的防御塔</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >20+不同关卡</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >30+种不同附魔和科技路线</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >带来丰富的游戏内容</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3287710/extras/207af92ac6aa7962de14ff37ead2b123.poster.avif?t=1731758461\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3287710/extras/207af92ac6aa7962de14ff37ead2b123.webm?t=1731758461\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3287710/extras/207af92ac6aa7962de14ff37ead2b123.mp4?t=1731758461\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >不同关卡体验</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在开始关卡前选择不同防御塔,附魔和科技路线，获得不同关卡体验</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3287710/extras/120523c221af5cf54d015f9220209ea3.poster.avif?t=1731758461\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3287710/extras/120523c221af5cf54d015f9220209ea3.webm?t=1731758461\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3287710/extras/120523c221af5cf54d015f9220209ea3.mp4?t=1731758461\" type=\"